                            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">ðŸ“‹ Terms of Service</h1>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Legal framework and user obligations for The Moment Connect platform</p>
                            <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">Effective Date: January 1, 2024 | Version 1.0</div>
