                        <div class="prose max-w-none">
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">By accessing and using The Moment Connect platform ("Service"), you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. If you do not agree to abide by the above, please do not use this service.</p>

                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Service Description</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The Moment Connect is a healthcare referral management platform that facilitates connections between:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
                                <li><strong>Agencies:</strong> Organizations submitting client referrals for treatment services</li>
                                <li><strong>Facilities:</strong> Treatment centers receiving and managing referral requests</li>
                                <li><strong>Administrators:</strong> System managers overseeing platform operations</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
                            
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">3.1 General Obligations</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
                                <li>Provide accurate and complete information</li>
                                <li>Maintain confidentiality of login credentials</li>
                                <li>Use the platform only for legitimate healthcare referral purposes</li>
                                <li>Comply with all applicable laws and regulations, including HIPAA</li>
                                <li>Report security incidents or data breaches immediately</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">3.2 Agency-Specific Responsibilities</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
                                <li>Verify client consent before submitting referrals</li>
                                <li>Provide accurate client assessment and needs information</li>
                                <li>Maintain current licensing and certification status</li>
                                <li>Follow up on referral outcomes as required</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">3.3 Facility-Specific Responsibilities</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
                                <li>Maintain accurate bed availability and capacity information</li>
                                <li>Respond to referrals within specified timeframes</li>
                                <li>Provide clear admission criteria and requirements</li>
                                <li>Update treatment outcomes and discharge information</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Prohibited Uses</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">You may not use the Service for:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
                                <li>Any unlawful purpose or to solicit others to perform unlawful acts</li>
                                <li>Violating any international, federal, provincial, or state regulations, rules, laws, or local ordinances</li>
                                <li>Infringing upon or violating our intellectual property rights or the intellectual property rights of others</li>
                                <li>Harassing, abusing, insulting, harming, defaming, slandering, disparaging, intimidating, or discriminating</li>
                                <li>Submitting false or misleading information</li>
                                <li>Uploading or transmitting viruses or any other type of malicious code</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Data Protection and Privacy</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The Moment Connect is committed to protecting user privacy and maintaining HIPAA compliance:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
                                <li>All protected health information (PHI) is encrypted in transit and at rest</li>
                                <li>Access controls ensure only authorized personnel can view sensitive data</li>
                                <li>Audit logs track all system access and data modifications</li>
                                <li>Business Associate Agreements (BAAs) are required for all covered entities</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">The Moment Connect provides a platform for healthcare referral management but does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Users are responsible for all clinical decisions and patient care. Our liability is limited to the maximum extent permitted by law.</p>

                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Service Availability</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">While we strive for 99.9% uptime, we do not guarantee uninterrupted service. Scheduled maintenance will be announced in advance. Emergency maintenance may occur without notice.</p>

                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Modifications to Terms</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Users will be notified of significant changes via email and platform notifications. Continued use of the service constitutes acceptance of modified terms.</p>

                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">9. Contact Information</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">For questions about these Terms of Service, contact:</p>
