                        <div class="prose max-w-none">
                            <h2 id="getting-started" class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Getting Started</h2>
                            
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">1.1 System Requirements</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
                                <li><strong>Browser:</strong> Chrome 90+, Firefox 88+, Safari 14+, Edge 90+</li>
                                <li><strong>Internet:</strong> Stable broadband connection (minimum 5 Mbps)</li>
                                <li><strong>Screen Resolution:</strong> Minimum 1024x768 (recommended 1920x1080)</li>
                                <li><strong>JavaScript:</strong> Must be enabled</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">1.2 Account Setup</h3>
                            <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4 mb-4">
                                <p class="text-green-700"><strong>Note:</strong> Account creation requires administrator approval and valid professional credentials.</p>
                            </div>
                            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
                                <li>Navigate to the registration page</li>
                                <li>Select your organization type (Agency or Facility)</li>
                                <li>Complete the registration form with accurate information</li>
                                <li>Upload required documentation (license, certifications)</li>
                                <li>Wait for administrator approval (typically 24-48 hours)</li>
                                <li>Check email for login credentials and setup instructions</li>
                            </ol>

                            <h2 id="admin-guide" class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Admin Dashboard Guide</h2>
                            
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">2.1 Dashboard Overview</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The Admin Dashboard provides system-wide oversight and management capabilities:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
                                <li><strong>System Metrics:</strong> Real-time statistics on agencies, facilities, and referrals</li>
                                <li><strong>User Management:</strong> Account approval, role assignment, and access control</li>
                                <li><strong>Referral Oversight:</strong> Monitor all referral activities and intervene when necessary</li>
                                <li><strong>Reporting:</strong> Generate compliance and performance reports</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">2.2 Key Functions</h3>
                            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
                                <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">User Account Management</h4>
                                <ul class="text-blue-800 text-sm space-y-1">
                                    <li>â€¢ Review and approve new account applications</li>
                                    <li>â€¢ Assign appropriate user roles and permissions</li>
                                    <li>â€¢ Suspend or deactivate accounts as needed</li>
                                    <li>â€¢ Reset passwords and manage security settings</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>

                            <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6">
                                <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-2">System Monitoring</h4>
