                            </div>

                            <h2 id="agency-guide" class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Agency Dashboard Guide</h2>
                            
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">3.1 Submitting Referrals</h3>
                            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
                                <li><strong>Client Assessment:</strong> Complete comprehensive ASAM assessment</li>
                                <li><strong>Documentation:</strong> Gather required medical and insurance information</li>
                                <li><strong>Referral Form:</strong> Complete all required fields in the referral submission form</li>
                                <li><strong>Priority Level:</strong> Assign appropriate priority (Critical, High, Standard)</li>
                                <li><strong>Submit:</strong> Review and submit referral for processing</li>
                            </ol>

                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">3.2 Tracking Referrals</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Monitor referral progress through these status stages:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
                                <li><strong>Submitted:</strong> Referral received and under initial review</li>
                                <li><strong>Processing:</strong> AI matching algorithm finding suitable facilities</li>
                                <li><strong>Matched:</strong> Potential facility matches identified</li>
                                <li><strong>Under Review:</strong> Facility reviewing referral details</li>
                                <li><strong>Accepted:</strong> Facility has accepted the referral</li>
                                <li><strong>Placed:</strong> Client successfully admitted to treatment</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h2 id="facility-guide" class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Facility Dashboard Guide</h2>
                            
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">4.1 Managing Capacity</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Maintain accurate bed availability information:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-2">
                                <li>Update bed counts daily or as changes occur</li>
                                <li>Specify bed types (detox, residential, outpatient)</li>
                                <li>Set admission criteria and restrictions</li>
                                <li>Update insurance acceptance and payment options</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">4.2 Reviewing Referrals</h3>
                            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4 mb-4">
                                <p class="text-yellow-700"><strong>Response Time:</strong> Facilities should respond to referrals within 4 hours during business hours.</p>
                            </div>
                            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
                                <li>Review client information and assessment details</li>
                                <li>Verify insurance coverage and authorization</li>
                                <li>Check bed availability for appropriate level of care</li>
                                <li>Accept or decline referral with detailed reasoning</li>
                                <li>If accepting, coordinate admission scheduling</li>
                            </ol>

